206: 
207: The explainer page teaches developers about FHE and confidential tokens using Three.js + React Three Fiber + drei. The goal is to be visually engaging while being very accessible — capture judges, not bore them. This is NOT redundant with the docs — the explainer TEACHES conceptually, the docs EXPLAIN implementation.
