230: ### Section 2: Wrapping (ERC-7984)
231: 
232: **Conceptual first:**
233: "ERC-7984 is the confidential version of ERC-20. Same interface, but balances are encrypted. Wrapping converts your public ERC-20 into a confidential ERC-7984 token. The original tokens are locked in the contract."
234: 
235: **Interactive moment:**
236: "Enter an amount to wrap." User types `50`. Clicks "Wrap." SDK `useEncrypt` encrypts the value. R3F animation shows encrypted handle appearing on-chain. "Your 50 USDC is now 50 cUSDC — encrypted. The blockchain sees this handle, not 50."
