774: - Hero section value props (3 cards: Discover / Wrap / Decrypt)
775: - "Why Official Pairs?" explainer on the registry page — visible when browsing pairs
776: - Comparison table in README — first thing judges see after the live demo link
777: - X thread addressing the fragmentation problem directly
778: - "Why not just deploy your own?" FAQ section in the app
779: - The app itself IS the argument — it demonstrates that official pairs work perfectly
