830: ## SDK Architecture
831: 
832: ### Initialization
833: 
834: Provider composition: WagmiProvider → QueryClientProvider → RainbowKitProvider → ZamaProvider → App [UPDATED: June 2026]
835: 
836: ZamaProvider config uses `web()` relayer transport which loads WASM from Zama CDN automatically via Web Worker. No vite-plugin-wasm needed.
837: 
838: ### Key Hooks
839: 
840: | Hook | Purpose |
841: |------|---------|
842: | ZamaProvider | App-level SDK context |
843: | useListPairs | Paginated registry pairs from on-chain |
844: | useMetadata | Token name/symbol/decimals (cached forever) |
845: | useShield | Wrap ERC-20 to ERC-7984 (auto-handles approval) |
846: | useUnshield | Unwrap ERC-7984 to ERC-20 (2-step async) |
847: | useResumeUnshield | Recover interrupted unwrap |
848: | useConfidentialBalance | Decrypt single balance |
849: | useConfidentialBalances | Batch decrypt |
850: | useGrantPermit | Sign EIP-712 permit (one-time per contract set) |
851: | useHasPermit | Gate decrypt calls |
852: | useDecryptValues | Decrypt handles to plaintext |
853: | useEncrypt | Encrypt plaintext to FHE ciphertext |
854: 
855: ### Critical Gotchas
856: 
857: - Always gate useConfidentialBalance with useHasPermit — no permit = unsolicited MetaMask popup
858: - EIP-712 timestamp must be Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000) — NOT milliseconds
859: - Decrypt batch limit: 2048 total encrypted bits per request
860: - FHE type mismatch causes InvalidType revert — frontend type must match contract's external type
861: - Unshield is 2-step — page close between steps requires useResumeUnshield
862: - Transport key pair expires after 30 days — need to re-grant permit
